<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XdYtQ3TCubHyzkUi7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXdYtQ3TCubHyzkUi7&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1ZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=aa02e715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XdYtQ3TCubHyzkUi7</a><br />\n<br />\nForwarded from telegram group"},{"pid":"377002ded8c7d1c41cb60782774df9cc2aee1425","tid":1497770,"uid":101151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7329d5ad3906a891fecdd8a00d7b4140ebe3d5d6","tid":1497770,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>聽日824對家吹大雞發動萬人圍港台<br />\n中共又發動宣傳機器想港台跪同清洗</strong><br />\n<br />\n營救香港電台！對家堅吹大雞萬人圍 配合國家機器滅利君雅鏗鏘集頭條新聞聲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afeaiKU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afeaiKU</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一人一信撐港台<br />\n去信廣管局</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fba_archives.ofca.gov.hk%2Fcn%2Fcontact%2F&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1ZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=86aa2341\" target=\"_blank\">https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依個唔算投訴，咪當意見咁send<br />\n記得話港台31,32台都有睇，做得好，最like咩節目同點解<br />\n唔好太黃絲feel 同唔好用standard form<br />\n會只當一份意見</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝瀏覽我們的網址。如有任何有關廣播事務的查詢，可按以下方式與我們聯絡： <br />\n<br />\n以電子郵件方式傳送至<br />\nba@tela.gov.hk<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3faRZNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3faRZNL.jpg&h=796e8d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以書面方式寄</strong><br />\n廣播事務管理局秘書處<br />\n經影視及娛樂事務管理處<br />\n香港灣仔告士打道5號<br />\n稅務大樓39樓<br />\n(傳真號碼：(852) 2507 2219)<br />\n<br />\n致電查詢電話號碼：(852) 2594 5721"}]}